-- Shares in Sinopec set to open down 3 pct after retail stake sale
-- 
-- Sun Sep 14, 2014 09:37PM EDT
-- None



HONG KONG, Sept 15 (Reuters) - Shares in Asia's top oil refiner Sinopec Corp <600028.SS> <0386.HK> was set to open 3 percent lower on Monday morning in Hong Kong after the company said it will sell a 107.1 billion yuan ($17.5 billion) stake in its retail unit. [ID:nL3N0RF0CU]

